{"type":"text","timestamp":1775843099918,"sessionID":"ses_28781ead6ffeH8TacWsajPyF7T","part":{"id":"prt_d787f1c49001GRYiUV99EOcXuV","messageID":"msg_d787edf61001sjsSKIR4OHzNmk","sessionID":"ses_28781ead6ffeH8TacWsajPyF7T","type":"text","text":"# AR-004 Archive Summary\n\n## What Was Completed\n\n### Core HTTP Service Framework ✓\n- **Server implementation** (`pkg/workloadmanager/server/server.go`): Gin-based HTTP server with graceful shutdown, health checks, and background garbage collection for expired/inactive sessions\n- **API endpoints**: POST `/v1/agent-runtime`, POST `/v1/code-interpreter`, GET `/v1/sessions/:sessionId`, DELETE `/v1/sessions/:sessionId`, GET `/health`\n- **Middleware stack** (`pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/middleware.go`): Recovery, logging, and CORS middleware\n\n### Session & Sandbox Management ✓\n- **Sandbox controller** (`pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go`): Creates Sandbox CRs from AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter specs, manages lifecycle, polls for pod IP readiness\n- **Session storage**: Integration with Redis for session metadata with expiration tracking\n- **Entry point management**: Builds protocol-aware endpoints (HTTP/TCP) for sandbox access\n\n### Configuration ✓\n- **Comprehensive config** (`pkg/workloadmanager/config/config.go`): Server, Redis, Kubernetes, auth, and session configuration with sensible defaults\n- **Config tests**: Basic validation tests included\n\n### Kubernetes Integration ✓\n- **Client wrapper** (`pkg/workloadmanager/client/k8s_client.go`): Dynamic client for CRD operations, pod IP retrieval (multiple strategies), sandbox lifecycle management\n- **Authentication** (`pkg/workloadmanager/auth/k8s_auth.go`): Kubernetes TokenReview integration with token caching\n\n### API Layer ✓\n- **Types and responses** (`pkg/workloadmanager/api/types.go`, `response.go`): Request/response structures, JSON helpers, error formatting\n- **Handler implementation** (`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/handler.go`): Request validation, error handling, response formatting\n\n## What Was Deferred\n\n### Testing (Partial)\n- ✓ 2 test files created (config_test.go, response_test.go)\n- ✗ Missing: Handler tests, middleware tests, controller tests, integration tests, E2E tests\n\n### Deployment & Operations\n- ✗ No main entry point or CLI (`cmd/workloadmanager/main.go` not created)\n- ✗ No Dockerfile or Kubernetes manifests (deployment.yaml, service.yaml)\n- ✗ No Prometheus metrics implementation\n- ✗ No comprehensive documentation (doc.go, README.md)\n\n### Security Features\n- ✗ Authentication middleware stubbed but not implemented\n- ✗ No RBAC enforcement middleware\n- ✗ No JWT token generation/validation (auth/jwt.go not created)\n\n### Advanced Features\n- ✗ Watch endpoints for CRDs\n- ✗ Request ID middleware\n- ✗ Metrics middleware\n- ✗ Readiness probe (only liveness/health implemented)\n- ✗ Rate limiting\n- ✗ Session keep-alive renewal\n\n### Code Quality\n- ✗ Implementation summary not updated (IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md template only)\n- ✗ Design documents incomplete (design.md, spec.md templates only)\n- ✗ No CHANGELOG entry\n\n### Summary\n**Completed**: ~60% of tasks - core HTTP service, sandbox/session management, K8s integration, basic middleware\n**Deferred**: Testing, deployment tooling, advanced security, observability, documentation","time":{"start":1775843099916,"end":1775843099916}}}
